* Version 0.1.3 (2013-01-17)
	- Added support for user to choose which language to extract.

* Version 0.1.2 (2012-09-20)
	- Added support for "big endian" files (Xbox 360).
	- Added option to manually specify the source folders in apply mode.
	- Fixed bug with the locals.bin file where whitespace was ignored.
	- Fixed bug in rebuilding certain .mul files.

* Version 0.1.1 (2012-07-26)
	- Changed subtitle search algorithm, now with less crashing!
	- Fixed bug where subtitles on separate lines were not reconstructed properly.

* Version 0.1.0
	- Initial release